<item>
            <title>[LU-11576] e2fck SIGSEGV at illegal extended attribute value</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11576</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;e2fsprogs-1.42.13.wc6-7.el7.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;nbp15-srv1 ~ # e2fsck -yf /dev/mapper/nbp15_1-MDT0 &lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck 1.42.13.wc6 (05-Feb-2017)&lt;br/&gt;
Pass 1: Checking inodes, blocks, and sizes&lt;br/&gt;
Inode 238990130 has illegal extended attribute value inode 778267756.&lt;br/&gt;
Fix? yes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Signal (11) SIGSEGV si_code=SEGV_MAPERR fault addr=0x7de7f9b0&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x42a0a1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libc.so.6(+0x362f0)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffecab32f0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libc.so.6(+0x16f015)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffecbec015&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libext2fs.so.2(+0x1a665)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffed6b4665&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libext2fs.so.2(+0x1a782)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffed6b4782&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libext2fs.so.2(ext2fs_attr_set+0x1b4)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffed6b5134&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x410b0a&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x410ba4&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck(e2fsck_pass1+0x2429)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x416ae9&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck(e2fsck_run+0x52)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x40eb22&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
e2fsck(main+0xcae)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x40a69e&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/lib64/libc.so.6(__libc_start_main+0xf5)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x7fffeca9f445&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
