                            <comment id="235619" author="pjones" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2018 22:31:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If the problem does not occur using the latest e2fsprogs (which is always recommended) doesn&apos;t that mean the ticket can be closed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
