                            <comment id="235611" author="adilger" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2018 20:35:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You could try e2fsprogs-1.44.3.wc1, which has a number of improvements for xattrs&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="235610" author="mhanafi" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2018 20:19:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are several filesystem having issue. the workaround for&#160; issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11574&quot; title=&quot;LustreError: 157-3: Trying to start OBD nbp13-OST000b_UUID using the wrong disk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11574&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11574&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; worked.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So this is a different filesystem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
