&lt;p&gt;Is this a different system down compared to that tracked by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11574&quot; title=&quot;LustreError: 157-3: Trying to start OBD nbp13-OST000b_UUID using the wrong disk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11574&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11574&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

